{
  "texts": [
    "Similar analyses were conducted to identify factors associated with false positives (i.e., DME labeled as present by ARIAS?",
    "no intraretinal and/or subretinal fluid on SD-OCT) in the subset of eyes without active DME on SD-OCT.",
    "The optimal cut-point for numerical covariates was determined using the cutpointr R package.",
    "Odds ratios (OR), 95% CI, and corresponding p-values were reported.",
    "The level of alpha = 0.10 was used to assess clinical significance."
  ]
}